Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:02.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Carnage!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.10,0:00:04.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}In Hindu mythology,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.19,0:00:07.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}it indicates the location of the battle\Nof Asura demigods and the King of Heaven,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.31,0:00:10.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}but at present, it's mainly used\Nto mean two other things.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.03,0:00:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The first is crunch time\Nright before a deadline.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.36,0:00:17.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}And the other...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.24,0:00:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an4}RUMBLE RUMBLE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.24,0:00:21.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}is a scene of difficulties\Nbetween two people!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.01,0:01:56.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Please eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.59,0:01:59.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Give me a break. You eat it, Shinomiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.05,0:02:02.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}KAGUYA WON'T FORGIVE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.51,0:02:03.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's my fault.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.52,0:02:06.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I hadn't eaten any...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.60,0:02:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Explaining this situation requires\Ntwo incidents to be touched on.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.48,0:02:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,THE FIRST INCIDENT:\N"THE KAGUYA HOME VISIT INCIDENT"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.90,0:02:17.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kaguya was out of it with a fever\Nwhen she pulled Shirogane into her bed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.90,0:02:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an4}SCOOP: KAGUYA HOME\NVISIT INCIDENT\NTHE CARETAKER\NWAS WATCHING!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.78,0:02:21.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}As a result, they slept next to each other\Nfor hours and nothing more,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.41,0:02:22.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}but when Kaguya came to her senses,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.99,0:02:25.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}she was justifiably bewildered\Nand flew into a rage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.62,0:02:29.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}However, an on-the-scene inspection\Nproved Shirogane innocent for the time being,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.92,0:02:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}and they handled it like adults.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:33.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I apologize for yelling at you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.04,0:02:34.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, it's my fault.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.38,0:02:37.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}They reconciled, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.80,0:02:39.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}there was still ill will!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.63,0:02:40.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}In Kaguya's point of view,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.84,0:02:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}he took advantage of her when she was\Nweakened with a cold, sharing her bed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.14,0:02:47.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe he touched her\Nwhen she was sleeping?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.93,0:02:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It made her feel uneasy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.44,0:02:51.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}And if he didn't do anything,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.48,0:02:53.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}that ticked her off, too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.31,0:02:54.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It made her feel dissatisfied.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.19,0:02:58.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}But as for Shirogane,\Nhe had a bone to pick, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.82,0:03:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}He was the one\Ndragged into Shinomiya's bed,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:03.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}and not only did she not understand\Na man's hardship{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:05.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}of exerting every iota of self-restraint,\Nbarely holding on,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.87,0:03:08.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}but she also continued\Nto view him with suspicion.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}So, it was only natural that he harbor\Nsome resentment toward her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.54,0:03:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}These feelings of discontent would continue\Nto mount, leading to an inevitable blowup.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.80,0:03:17.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,THE SECOND INCIDENT:\N"THE CAKE INCIDENT"!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.21,0:03:20.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}EARLIER
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:20.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.09,0:03:24.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's from the headmaster.\NHelp yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.27,0:03:29.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This is all the cake there is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.39,0:03:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I wish the headmaster\Nwere more considerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:35.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He should've at least given us\Nenough for all the members.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.77,0:03:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, earlier, you and I\Nwere the only ones here, President, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.57,0:03:43.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Eat up, Ishigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.07,0:03:44.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't need any.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.03,0:03:45.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, please have it, President.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:49.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's okay. You eat it, Shinomiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:51.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, no, you, President.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.41,0:03:52.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, really, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.67,0:03:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, I insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.54,0:03:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I insist!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:55.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, I insist!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:01.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Just eat it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.63,0:04:03.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You should eat it, President!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.55,0:04:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Discontent. This is where it blows up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.76,0:04:13.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an4}ONE MINUTE LATER
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.39,0:04:09.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Girls like this kind of thing,\Nso don't hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.97,0:04:13.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You don't have an aversion to sweets,\Ndo you, President? So, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.89,0:04:13.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Essentially polite,\Nwilling to give up their share.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.27,0:04:15.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Look, while you're arguing,\Nit's getting mushy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.27,0:04:20.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an4}FIVE MINUTES LATER
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:20.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}But as the minutes passed,\Nit entered into a new phase.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:17.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes, right.\NAnd it's almost time to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:20.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm a slow eater,\Nso by all means, President.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.65,0:04:23.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My hand's already getting tired\Nfrom holding this plate!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:23.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}20 MINUTES LATER
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:26.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you eat it, this whole issue\Nwould be settled peacefully, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:28.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're so stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:28.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}ONE HOUR LATER
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.91,0:04:30.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Would you just eat it, already?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.66,0:04:34.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,There's no need for you\Nto be so obstinate here, President.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.83,0:04:38.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}After an hour of this, no one would object\Nto it being called "a scene of carnage."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:41.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The place had turned into\Nan underworld of mingled resentment!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.05,0:04:44.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The cake wants you\Nto eat it, too, President!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.26,0:04:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}It's my fault.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:47.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}If I hadn't eaten a piece,\Nthis never would've happened.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:47.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Use common sense when you speak!\NCake can't talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.14,0:04:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Prove to me that cake can't talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:51.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}This has become a disaster.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.56,0:04:52.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Extraordinary claims\Nrequire extraordinary proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:52.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}I've got it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:54.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fujiwara-senpai!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.35,0:04:59.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fujiwara-senpai is the only one\Nwho can stop those two!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.61,0:05:03.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why are you being so pigheaded\Nabout not eating it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,There's a limit\Nto how stubborn one can be!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:08.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes, I admit to being stubborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:10.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But it's because of something\Nyou said before, Shinomiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:13.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Just what did I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:16.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It was right after we both started\Nin the student council!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.71,0:05:20.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do you have any hobbies, Shinomiya?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:23.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, but is that any of your business?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.92,0:05:24.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not really.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.72,0:05:29.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's just that your eyes are so lifeless.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was wondering\Nif there was anything that you liked.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:35.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Something I like...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.77,0:05:38.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Shortcake.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:40.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's what you said!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.52,0:05:42.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I could never forget that face!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.03,0:05:48.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Why would you remember\Nsomething so trivial from that long ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.66,0:05:50.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}How could I forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:53.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Is that right? Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:55.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}The tip of my nose itches!\NI'm going to scratch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.54,0:05:57.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't mind me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.04,0:05:58.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sure, scratch all you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.25,0:06:06.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}He remembered from that long ago.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.68,0:06:10.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If that's your story,\Nthen I've got one, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.85,0:06:11.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.51,0:06:13.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The end of last year!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:18.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}What are you going to do\Nfor Christmas, President?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:21.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Work.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.19,0:06:22.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, really?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.15,0:06:24.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's tough.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.36,0:06:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not especially.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.49,0:06:29.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}To me, Christmas is just another day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.99,0:06:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}My old man gives me a gift certificate\Nfor 2,000 yen worth of books. That's it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:39.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}We don't really celebrate,\Nand I've never had Christmas cake.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not that I'm envious or anything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.21,0:06:46.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hearing that made me kind of sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.84,0:06:51.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You've never been able to have it before,\Nso I want you to eat this cake, President!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:56.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You remember that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.93,0:06:59.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Is that right? Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.27,0:07:02.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Actually, my forehead itches!\NNever mind me while I scratch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.73,0:07:04.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Scratch away! I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.86,0:07:10.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.45,0:07:12.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Since it's come to this, I have an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:15.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,For today only, I'll feed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, just the opposite!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:20.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'll feed you, Shinomiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.41,0:07:22.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Please don't steal my feeding idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't be shy! Just open your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:26.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You open your mouth, Shinomiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:31.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Open wide!\N- Open wide!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.51,0:07:37.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}This isn't getting us anywhere!\NYou have a bite, and then I'll have a bite!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.39,0:07:40.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}No, you go first! If you eat it, I'll eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:42.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}No complaints if we eat\Nat the same time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}That's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:48.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}GRR GRR
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.65,0:07:48.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:08:00.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This is the Friend Police!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Are you the naughty kids\Nwho've been fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.67,0:08:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}NO FIGHTING!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.09,0:08:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}IF YOU CAN'T GET ALONG,\NI'LL CONFISCATE YOUR CAKE!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:16.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Results of today's match...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:18.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}RESULTS OF TODAY'S MATCH:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:18.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kaguya and Shirogane lose.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:18.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5}KAGUYA AND SHIROGANE LOSE
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:22.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}WAR CRIMINAL
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:22.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,MMM, YUMMY
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:26.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Romantic advice?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.52,0:08:30.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Well, it's not really romantic, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.86,0:08:32.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}KAGUYA WANTS TO FORGIVE
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:32.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}advice about the opposite sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.57,0:08:36.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Um, like a good way to make up with someone\Nof the opposite sex you had a fight with.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:40.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Since you have a boyfriend,\NMiss Kashiwagi,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I thought maybe you'd have\Nsome useful advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:52.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:08:54.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're asking me for romantic advice?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:57.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Well, not exactly romantic,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.30,0:08:58.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I want to see if you know a way
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.60,0:09:01.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}to make peace with someone\Nof the opposite sex you had a fight with.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:05.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I see. In that case,\Nyou've come to the right person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:08.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm the Love Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:09.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.61,0:09:10.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:11.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:15.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But I do read a lot of romcom manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:17.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I guess that would work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm asking for a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.99,0:09:23.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}When you put it like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.83,0:09:26.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}it sounds like you're talking\Nabout yourself, President.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:29.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}But you wouldn't be that clichéd,\Nwould you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:30.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yeah, right, as if.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:33.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:38.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So, Miss Shinomiya, what were you\Nand this person fighting about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.93,0:09:40.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.72,0:09:43.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,By the way, I'm asking for a friend.\NIt's not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.35,0:09:45.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is definitely about Miss Shinomiya.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.56,0:09:49.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A friend of mine, a girl,\Ncame down with a cold,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:52.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,and then, a boy visited her at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.15,0:09:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But while she was delirious\Nwith a fever...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.53,0:09:58.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.37,0:10:01.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I guess you could say they slept together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.28,0:10:05.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,When she woke up,\Nthe boy was in bed next to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.46,0:10:09.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's terrible! Shameless!\NWhat a brute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.29,0:10:10.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.13,0:10:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,nothing happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:18.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,In fact, the girl was so out of it\Nthat it's possible she initiated...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.84,0:10:19.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Even so!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.97,0:10:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's especially when a girl\Nis in a weakened state
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.05,0:10:25.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,that the man must have morals\Nand not do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.39,0:10:28.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I agree. That's the correct way\Nto see it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:31.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That boy doesn't have any morals, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.19,0:10:33.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Right? Right? Right? Right?\NRight? Right? Right? Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.19,0:10:33.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}RIGHT!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.77,0:10:37.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What's wrong with that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She sounds like a lunatic!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.41,0:10:43.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What kind of woman invites you into her bed,\Nthen berates you the next morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.45,0:10:45.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sounds like she's got no morals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.49,0:10:48.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That woman sounds like\Na real pain in the ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.29,0:10:51.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,In a romcom, she'd be the standard\Nblack-haired, flat-chested type.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.17,0:10:53.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Typical, typical.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.50,0:10:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Incredible. Once he gets going,\Nhe doesn't stop.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.46,0:10:57.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Being loopy with a fever is no excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.05,0:10:59.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I mean, she pulled a dude into bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.43,0:11:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bet you anything she's a nympho.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.84,0:11:05.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,At a glance, she's prim and proper,\Nnot to mention stuck-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.18,0:11:07.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The way she expresses\Nher sexual desire is twisted, selfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.47,0:11:10.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She says, "I'm not interested in men,"\Nbut with a handsome guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,she'll get her teeth into him\Nin no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.69,0:11:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If a man is a wolf,\Nthen, a woman's a snake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.19,0:11:15.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Quick to get entangled\Nand swallows the tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.82,0:11:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ouroboros, I'm telling you!\NNot me! Not this cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:20.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sure after the guy left, she rubbed—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.57,0:11:22.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay, hit the brakes, Ishigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:27.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Look, even so, the guy really\Nshouldn't have gone along with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:32.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,There had to be a gentle way\Nof getting out of it, but he just didn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:34.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.88,0:11:36.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}He probably didn't want to get out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:39.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Fight!\N- Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.97,0:11:44.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But they apologized to each other\Nabout it, so it's settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.97,0:11:52.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The thing is, after that, the boy acted\Ntotally normal as if nothing had happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:54.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I feel you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.48,0:11:59.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The girl is like on pins and needles,\Nwhile the guy has already moved on...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:02.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}when it wasn't just some minor mishap.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.99,0:12:04.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.82,0:12:10.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So, it's only natural for her\Nto be a little annoyed with him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:13.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,In the first place,\Nthey were in the same bed,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.96,0:12:17.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,so the man should take responsibility\Nand tell her how he feels about her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:19.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Th-That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.42,0:12:21.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}He's being too irresponsible, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.01,0:12:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Right? Right? Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.72,0:12:24.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Shut up, you moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,They apologized to each other, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:29.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then, it should be over and done with!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:31.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why the hell is she dragging it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's so loud.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Just hearing that pisses me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.36,0:12:37.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}How about if I give\Nthat woman a talking-to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.23,0:12:40.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'll tell her what time it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.19,0:12:40.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:43.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,that's fine as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.20,0:12:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She doesn't want him\Nto take responsibility or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.24,0:12:49.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then, what's to be angry about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.41,0:12:53.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}What's to be... angry about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.16,0:13:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}If he didn't lay a finger on you and you\Ndon't want him to take responsibility...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:03.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,then, what's to be angry about,\NMiss Shinomiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:07.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I can't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:10.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just can't say it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.64,0:13:13.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}That I actually wanted him\Nto do something, just a little!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.73,0:13:14.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.10,0:13:16.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Am I really that unappealing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.89,0:13:16.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm sorry. I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.23,0:13:19.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't tell her I'm angry\Nabout something that silly!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:22.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Of course I can't tell anyone about that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.65,0:13:25.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}That? Th-Th-That?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.74,0:13:29.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's how a guy should be like when\Na woman is pissed about some trivial thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.58,0:13:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Anyway, for a man to try to understand\Neverything about a woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.41,0:13:34.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,it's probably just a fool's errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:39.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,In the end, your friend\Nshould just chill out until the heat's off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.09,0:13:43.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If he doesn't have anything\Nto feel guilty about,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:46.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,then there's no need for him to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:50.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Nothing to feel guilty about, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.07,0:14:10.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Shinomiya, there's something\NI have to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.03,0:14:13.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.37,0:14:17.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I told you I didn't lay a finger on you,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.75,0:14:20.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,the truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:22.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I did lay just one finger on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.10,0:14:32.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Where did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.35,0:14:35.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,touch me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:36.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Your lips.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.15,0:14:43.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I maybe just tapped them\Nwith my pointer finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.73,0:14:46.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I mean, not in any weird sense\Nor like a prank or—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.78,0:14:47.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,President...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:53.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Now we're even.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.92,0:15:09.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Starting tomorrow,\Nwe'll be back to normal, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.05,0:15:11.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:30.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Results of today's match...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:32.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}RESULTS OF TODAY'S MATCH:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.28,0:15:32.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}They both won.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.28,0:15:32.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}THEY BOTH WON\N(SUCCESSFULLY MADE UP)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.16,0:15:35.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}PASSING BY
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:35.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}HUH...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.12,0:15:40.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Great work, student council!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.41,0:15:43.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}And it's summer vacation\Nstarting tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.17,0:15:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}- Yay!\N- Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.54,0:15:46.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}RUSTLE RUSTLE
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:49.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Do you have any special plans,\NShinomiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.67,0:15:53.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Go shopping a little is about all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.26,0:15:55.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Will you be busy working, President?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.22,0:15:57.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.22,0:16:00.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}MIYUKI SHIROGANE\NWANTS TO GO SOMEWHERE
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:15:59.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}When they adjusted the schedule,\Nthey kind of short-sheeted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.98,0:16:02.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}That leaves me\Nwith a lot of time on my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.44,0:16:04.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'd like to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.61,0:16:06.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes, I'd like to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.57,0:16:08.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Right, Fujiwara?\N- Right, Miss Fujiwara?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.82,0:16:12.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}SUMMER VACATION PLANS!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.11,0:16:12.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Summer vacation plans!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Mountains!\N- Beach!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.61,0:16:14.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mt. Osore!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.91,0:16:19.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The topic of a trip was discussed once\Nbut ended up getting put off.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.83,0:16:21.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Will it come to nothing or be carried out?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.25,0:16:25.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The moment had come\Nto make that decision.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.71,0:16:28.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}There are many events that take place\Nduring summer vacation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.71,0:16:30.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an6}AUGUST
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.71,0:16:33.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an4}TRIP\NFIREWORKS\NSUMMER FESTIVAL\NBBQ\NBEACH
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Whether a coed group\Ngoes to these events together{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:33.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}all depends on whether\Nthey get off to a good start.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.22,0:16:36.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}By going somewhere together\Nfor the first time...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.43,0:16:39.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Where should we go next?"\N"Let's all go somewhere again."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.18,0:16:40.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}And that opens up possibilities.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.35,0:16:43.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the other hand,\Nif they stumble at the start,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.85,0:16:46.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}the psychological hurdle\Nfor a coed plan becomes higher!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.86,0:16:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Boys will stick with the boys,\Ngirls with the girls,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.07,0:16:51.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}and that's how they'll spend\Nsummer vacation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.24,0:16:55.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}If they fail here,\Nit'll be a gray summer vacation!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.99,0:16:59.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}THE GIRL'S SANDAL BREAKS,\NAND I MUST CARRY HER
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.99,0:17:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}No! No! No! No! No! No!\NNo! No! No! No! No! No!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.49,0:16:59.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an6}TEST OF COURAGE
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.03,0:17:02.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5}GOING HOME\NTO THE COUNTRY\NAND SEEING YOUR\NCHILDHOOD FRIEND
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.49,0:17:02.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}TIME LEAPS AND\NDIFFERENT DIMENSION\NSUMMONS
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.99,0:17:02.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an4}ONE-SUMMER\NADVENTURES\NARE SURELY\NNOT POSSIBLE
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.99,0:17:02.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}DOING\NHOMEWORK\NTOGETHER
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.00,0:17:03.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an6}LOVEY-DOVEY\NWORDS THAT GET\NMUTED THROUGH\NEXPLODING\NFIREWORKS
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:03.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}GOING ON\NCOED TRIPS\NTOGETHER
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:03.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5}OH NO,\NI NEED\NTO DO CPR
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:03.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}FINDING LOVE\NAT THE TEMP JOB
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.08,0:17:03.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nooo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.08,0:17:03.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an4}SWIMSUITS AND BBQ\NAT THE BEACH
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:05.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Reality!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.50,0:17:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's what reality is!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:10.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}A trip with Shinomiya?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:12.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Of course I wanna go!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.05,0:17:17.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}But if I bring up the idea of a trip here...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.80,0:17:22.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, President...\NAre you bringing up that again?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.73,0:17:27.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was like a one-shot topic. I mean,\Nit wasn't a serious conversation, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.73,0:17:31.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Are you really thinking of going?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:34.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Did you have your heart set on that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.74,0:17:36.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}How cute.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.49,0:17:37.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an4}AAAH
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.74,0:17:37.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}That would happen!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.24,0:17:41.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Summer! Summer! Summer vacation!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.24,0:17:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're the one who brought up a trip!\NWhat are you doing just dancing around?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.45,0:17:44.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Summer vacation! Summer vacation!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.20,0:17:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fujiwara!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:45.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Summer is the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.87,0:17:48.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}when you wanna just go all out\Nand spread your wings, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:50.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an4}DI... VERSION
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.50,0:17:53.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Right! Summer is the time you wanna\Ndo something you usually can't do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.26,0:17:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Like a trip would be great!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.76,0:17:56.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Yeah, that's it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.72,0:17:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}A trip, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.05,0:18:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sure, everyone needs time away from\Nthe hustle and bustle of life in the city, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.85,0:18:02.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.81,0:18:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm going to Hawaii for about a week!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.18,0:18:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}This is gonna work!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.48,0:18:10.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}You can go to hell!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.44,0:18:13.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}You're the one who said before\Nyou wanted to go on a trip with everyone!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.86,0:18:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}What's the idea of taking the lead\Nand acting like you're Hawaiian?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.28,0:18:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aloha in Honolulu!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.28,0:18:20.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Shinomiya, she's your whatever,\Nisn't she? Do something!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.95,0:18:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.37,0:18:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A trip... is a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:26.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kaguya also understands the importance{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.54,0:18:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}of getting off to a good start\Nfor summer vacation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}However, she's known Fujiwara\Nfor a long time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.92,0:18:36.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}and thus realizes there is no chance\Nthat Fujiwara will behave to one's satisfaction.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.63,0:18:40.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Therefore, there is nothingness!\NThe empty mind that has checked out!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.89,0:18:42.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Breathing is fun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.76,0:18:46.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an4}NOTHING...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.68,0:18:46.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}It's no use! I don't sense\Nany drive in Shinomiya!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.85,0:18:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}W-Well, if Fujiwara is going on a trip,\Nthat's all she wrote.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.98,0:18:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}The idea of all of us going somewhere\Non a trip was a tall order to begin with.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.90,0:18:56.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}But at least...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.44,0:18:59.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}At least go somewhere\Non a day trip and have fun!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.45,0:19:00.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.78,0:19:03.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go somewhere without Miss Fujiwara?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.78,0:19:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}In other words, you want to go somewhere\Nwith me and not with Miss Fujiwara?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.54,0:19:09.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh my.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.17,0:19:11.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}How cute.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:13.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm checkmated!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:13.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an4}AAAH
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Without Fujiwara,\Nit won't get off the ground!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.01,0:19:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Aloha! Honolulu!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.59,0:19:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can she do something like a week\Nafter she gets back from her trip?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.47,0:19:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Fujiwara...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.05,0:19:25.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A trip abroad is fine,\Nbut so is a trip here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.93,0:19:27.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,There are a lot of events during summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.77,0:19:29.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.31,0:19:36.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}SERIOUS SERIOUS
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:33.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Second-year summer is crunch time\Nfor university entrance exams!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.19,0:19:35.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I don't have time\Nto fritter away on having fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.61,0:19:36.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}You asshole!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.82,0:19:39.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You'd say that when you're the one\Nwho's going on a trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.53,0:19:43.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Exactly! I'm keeping a balance\Nbetween work and play!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.16,0:19:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dammit! That's a fair argument!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.99,0:19:46.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}President, don't bother.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:50.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}You'll never be able to control Fujiwara.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.29,0:19:54.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}At a time like this, I think about yummy food.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.17,0:19:59.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Crap! I planned to win\NShinomiya's heart this summer!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.97,0:20:03.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}How cute.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.97,0:20:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whatever pattern I attack,\Nthat's how it ends up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.56,0:20:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it a lost cause?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.35,0:20:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But I'd like to do something\Nto make memories, even just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ishigami?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.19,0:20:16.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm a first-year,\Nand you're a second-year, President.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Maybe next year, with studying\Nfor university entrance exams,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.36,0:20:24.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}there won't be time for anything.\NMaybe this is the only year we could hang out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.57,0:20:25.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Ishigami...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.99,0:20:28.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is what you've been thinking?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.87,0:20:33.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right. Summer isn't\Njust about hanging out with girls.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Having dumb fun with guy friends...\NThat's summer, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:41.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's go, Ishigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.13,0:20:43.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,There's a big festival\Nat the end of summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.01,0:20:46.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I can treat you to takoyaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.05,0:20:46.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Summer festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.93,0:20:49.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.22,0:20:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}What happened to crunch time?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.10,0:20:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's a great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.56,0:20:53.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cotton candy! The shooting game!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.06,0:20:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fireworks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.35,0:20:55.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fireworks?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.36,0:20:57.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fireworks with the president?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.82,0:20:59.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm in!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.61,0:21:03.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The festival is on August 24th, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.03,0:21:05.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll keep my schedule open.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.78,0:21:07.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes, me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.74,0:21:12.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wait. I can't make it. I'll be\Nin Spain then for the tomato festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.58,0:21:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go to the festival in hell, idiot!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.29,0:21:15.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}How many trips are you taking?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.83,0:21:19.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh no! Worldly desires! Worldly desires!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:19.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Her empty mind collapsed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.21,0:21:22.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you're gonna go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.01,0:21:23.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.18,0:21:29.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You guys would be so mean to go\Nto a summer festival without me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.06,0:21:31.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yeah, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.27,0:21:36.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're going to the tomato festival,\Naren't you, Fujiwara-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.27,0:21:39.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're gonna have fun there,\Nbut telling us not to go? Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.86,0:21:46.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}WAAAAH
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.07,0:21:46.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're so mean to me, Ishigami!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.61,0:21:49.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Idiot! Cold-blooded human!\NYour bangs are too long!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.12,0:21:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ishigami, I hope you burn\Nyour tongue on a takoyaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.88,0:21:59.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I did it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.05,0:22:03.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.84,0:22:08.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wait, Ishigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.05,0:22:09.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You were in the right today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.26,0:22:12.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Results of today's match...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.26,0:22:15.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an6}RESULTS OF TODAY'S MATCH:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.01,0:22:14.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Victory for everyone except for Fujiwara.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.01,0:22:15.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}VICTORY FOR EVERYONE EXCEPT FOR FUJIWARA\N(FOR SUCCESSFULLY MAKING A PLAN\NTO GO TO THE SUMMER FESTIVAL)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.39,0:22:18.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, let's meet there on that day at 7 pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.23,0:22:19.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.94,0:22:24.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}And so, we embark on a new chapter!\NMen and women's summer vacation!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.95,0:22:29.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}OH NO
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.57,0:22:29.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an6}PADDED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.20,0:22:29.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}I SEE...
